translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ぴったりの当店の品揃え、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Our store's selection is just perfect,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 是非見てってやー！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Please be sure to take a look!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「おっ、そこの可愛らしいお嬢ちゃん！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Hey, you cute young lady over there!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: そーそー、あんたや、あんた！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Yes, yes, you! Yes, you!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: あなたは呼び止められて振り返った。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: You were called out to and turned around.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「あんさんみたいな素敵なレディに
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: For a wonderful lady like you,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ぴったりの当店の品揃え、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: our store's selection is just perfect,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 是非見てってやー！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: please be sure to take a look!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 言われた通り、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: As she said,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: あなたは軒先の商品に目をやった。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: you looked at the goods displayed at the shop's entrance.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: いまいちあなたにはよく分からないが、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: You didn't quite understand it clearly,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: どうやらすごい品が揃っているようだ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: but it seemed like they had an amazing selection.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ウチ、なんでも屋ですねん。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "We're a general store,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ただし普通のなんでも屋と違うて、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: but unlike ordinary general stores,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: レア品ばっか取りそろえてまんねん」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: we stock only rare items."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「その分、普通のGOLDでは
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Because of that, you can't exchange with regular GOLD—

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 交換できまへんで〜」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: you can't do it with normal GOLD~"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ズバリ！　金塊だけで交換承っておりますねん！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Exactly! We only accept gold bars for exchanges!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「あんさんも、金塊持ってたら、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "If you have gold bars,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 是非是非交換しておくれやすー。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: please, by all means, exchange with us.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: どーせ他に使い道もないでしょうし〜」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Anyway, you probably have no other use for them~"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: あなたも金塊を持っていれば、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: If you also have gold bars,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: レアなアイテムと交換してもらえるだろう。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: you could likely exchange them for rare items.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「おい、＜エール＞」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Hey, <Aile>"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「まったく、なにしてんだよ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Really, what are you doing?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: こんなあからさまな客引きに引っかかって。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Falling for such obvious customer solicitation.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ほれ、行くぞ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Come on, let's go."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: あなたは長田君に引っ張られた。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: You were pulled along by Nagata-kun.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「あーあー、ええどすええどす。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Ah, ah, that’s fine, that’s fine.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: また時間があるときに、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Whenever you have time again,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: いつでも来ておくれやすー」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: please come by anytime~"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「金塊沢山集めての来店、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "We look forward to your visit with lots of gold bars,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: お待ちしてるでごわすー」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: we'll be waiting for you~"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: あなた達は近場で見つけた屋台通りから
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: You and your companions picked some products from a nearby street of food stalls,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 適当な商品を見繕い、広場で食事をしていた。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: and were eating in the square.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「はむっ、んぐっ、むぐっ……！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Chomp, gulp, munch...!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: んーっ、美味いなー！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Mmm, this is delicious!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 砂漠踏破の間も摂っていたのは
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: During the desert crossing, you had only been eating

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 軽食くらいだったあなたは、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: light snacks,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: もりもりと串焼きを平らげていく。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: and now you were voraciously devouring skewers.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「はぐっ、はぐっ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Nom, nom.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: そういや、なんも聞いてなかったっすけど、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: By the way, I just realized I never asked,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: リセット・カラーってどんな人なんすか？」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: what kind of person is Reset Color?"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「リセット様だすか……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Reset-sama, you say...?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ロッキーは食べていた豆のスープを
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Rocky placed the bean soup he was eating

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 膝の上に置いて、遠い目をした。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: on his lap and looked into the distance.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「おらが知ってるのは、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "What I know about her

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: まだ彼女が幼かった頃のことだけだすが……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: is only from when she was still a child..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「一言で言えば、素直な良い子だすな。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "In a word, she's an honest, good girl.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 周りに好かれる天真爛漫な方でしただ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: She was a bright and cheerful person loved by those around her.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ちょっとお転婆なのが玉に瑕だすが……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "She was a little tomboyish, which was her only flaw...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「きっと今頃は強く美しく育ってる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I'm sure by now she has grown strong and beautiful.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ことと思うだす」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: That's what I believe."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ふーん」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Hmm."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「それにランス様と共に冒険をしたことのある
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Moreover, she is the only child of the Demon Lord who has adventured with Lord Rance.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 唯一の魔王のお子様だ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: She is the unique Demon Lord's child.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 仲間になってくれればきっと心強いだすよ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: If she joins us, she'll surely be a powerful ally."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「じゃあ、やっぱり仲間にするのは
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Then, it seems we definitely should aim to make her a comrade!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 目指した方が良さそっすね！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: That's the way to go, right!?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「うーっし！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Alright!"
